e South Bank district of London, just north of Waterloo Station. It is owned by the British Film Institute and since July 2012 has been operated by Odeon Cinemas.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Watching a film here is a completely immersive experience and our programme ranges from the latest IMAX blockbusters to world-class alternative content and educational presentations.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:11:"IMAX Cinema";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:11:"london-imax";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-05-23 14:45:09";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-10-22 18:27:06";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:76:"https://pixelgrade.com/demos/listable-stock/?post_type=job_listing&amp;p=514";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:11:"job_listing";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:1;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:931;s:11:"post_author";s:2:"29";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2015-04-06 14:40:05";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2015-11-04 22:21:16";s:12:"post_content";s:770:"<p style="text-align: justify;">Movie-loving New Yorkers can enjoy delicious food and cold drinks above the city streets, before catching their favourite classic, cult and current movie in the glow of the iconic skyline.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">With state-of-the-art equipment, high-quality wireless headphones and comfy seats in a truly unique urban environment, these are movie screenings with altitude.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Since its inception in 2011, Rooftop Film Club has pioneered the outdoor cinema phenomenon in the UK, becoming a staple of the London culture scene. In the years since Rooftop Film Club has grown a sizable and passionate following, selling out over 250 rooftop screenings across five London venues in 2014 alone.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:17:"Rooftop Film Club";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"rooftop-film-club";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-04-06 14:40:05";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-11-04 22:21:16";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:76:"https://pixelgrade.com/demos/listable-stock/?post_type=job_listing&amp;p=931";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:11:"job_listing";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:2;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:526;s:11:"post_author";s:2:"29";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2015-03-06 17:42:58";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2015-10-22 19:17:14";s:12:"post_content";s:763:"<p style="text-align: justify;">The iconic London Palladium is the perfect venue to host the grandest business conferences, presentations, meetings and receptions. This prestigious theatre’s auditorium seats over 2,200 people, while two bars offer spaces to fit smaller business functions. The London Palladium is situated in the heart of London’s West End, a short walk from Oxford Circus.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">From the roster of stars who have played there and many televised performances, it is arguably the most famous theatre in London and the United Kingdom, especially for musical variety shows. The theatre has also hosted the Royal Variety Performance a record 40 times, most recently in 2014.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>";s:10:"post_title";s:17:"Palladium Theater";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:24:"london-palladium-theater";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-03-06 17:42:58";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-10-22 19:17